<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: active mechanites addiction -->
  <GR_ElectroEggAddiction.label>活化型纳米机械成瘾</GR_ElectroEggAddiction.label>
  <!-- EN: A chemical addiction to active mechanites. Long-term presence of active mechanites has caused neurological adaptations at the cellular level, so the brain can no longer function properly without them.\n\nWithout regular doses of active mechanites, withdrawal symptoms will begin. However, extended abstinence will force the brain to adapt back to its normal state, resolving the addiction. -->
  <GR_ElectroEggAddiction.description>长期过量的摄取活化型纳米机械已经造成了神经系统的适应。\n\n如果没有定期摄取合适数量的机械蛋，戒断反应就会开始。长时间的戒断会迫使大脑适应并恢复到正常状态，从而戒除活化型纳米机械成瘾。</GR_ElectroEggAddiction.description>
  <!-- EN: withdrawal -->
  <GR_ElectroEggAddiction.stages.withdrawal.label>戒断反应</GR_ElectroEggAddiction.stages.withdrawal.label>
  
  <!-- EN: high on active mechanites -->
  <GR_ElectroEggHigh.label>活化型纳米机械亢奋</GR_ElectroEggHigh.label>
  <!-- EN: Active mechanites in the bloodstream. They lift the mood and increase attentiveness. -->
  <GR_ElectroEggHigh.description>流淌在血液里的活化型纳米机械。它能够增强意识与新陈代谢，并提供心情增益。</GR_ElectroEggHigh.description>
  <!-- EN: an active mechanites high -->
  <GR_ElectroEggHigh.labelNoun>活化型纳米机械亢奋</GR_ElectroEggHigh.labelNoun>
  
  <!-- EN: active mechanites tolerance -->
  <GR_ElectroEggTolerance.label>活化型纳米机械耐受</GR_ElectroEggTolerance.label>
  <!-- EN: A built-up tolerance to active mechanites. The more severe this tolerance is, the more active mechanites it takes to get the same effect. -->
  <GR_ElectroEggTolerance.description>对活化型纳米机械的长期耐受性。耐受性越严重，想达到和之前同样的效果所需要的机械蛋也就越多。</GR_ElectroEggTolerance.description>
  <!-- EN: small -->
  <GR_ElectroEggTolerance.stages.small.label>弱</GR_ElectroEggTolerance.stages.small.label>
  <!-- EN: large -->
  <GR_ElectroEggTolerance.stages.large.label>强</GR_ElectroEggTolerance.stages.large.label>
  <!-- EN: massive -->
  <GR_ElectroEggTolerance.stages.massive.label>极强</GR_ElectroEggTolerance.stages.massive.label>
  
</LanguageData>